customization-customize-share-link.html.body:
Customize share link
If you want to replace any default share parameters — edit social network provider and re-build script.
export const vkontakte_share = new Vkontakte(
    'http://example.com/', // URL
    'New title of current page', // title
    'New description of current page.', // description
    'http://example.com/path/to/new-image.jpg' // image
).shareWindow();


Please keep in mind, not all social networks support all of them share parameters!

customization-customize-share-count.html.body:
Customize share counter
If you want to replace default share counter URL — edit social network provider and re-build script.
export const vkontakte_counter = new Vkontakte(
    'http://example.com/' // URL
).getCounter();


Please keep in mind, not all social networks supports share counter!
